      "text": "ar farweim Tehweem / un tappe bi/ es tewis pehz to Kehniu bil-\nDahwida Pilli aprakts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un tahs Deenas/ kamehr\nDahwids Kehniſch bijis pahr\nIſraelu/ irr ticheirdefinitis Gad-\ndi/ ſeptin Gaddus bij wiſch Ge-\nbronā waldis/ un trihsdefinitis\nun trihs Gaddus Jeruſalemē.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Un Salamans fehdeja us\nfawa Tehwa Dahwida Gohda-\nKrehſlu/ un wiſcha Walstiba tap-\npe warren ſtiprinata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un Adonijus Agitas\nDehls/ nahze pee Batſebas Sa-\nlamana Mahtes. Un ta ſazzija:\nArrig tu ar Meeru nahz? un\nwiſch ſazzija: Ar Meeru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Wehl ſazzija wiſch:\nMan ar tew kas jarunna. Un\nwiſna ſazzija: Runna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Tad ſazzija wiſch: Tu\nfiinni/ ka man ta Walstiba pee-\nderreja/ un wiſſas Iſraela Azziſ\nus man raundsija/ ka man bij par\nKehnizu buht/ bet nu irr ta Wal-\nstiba nowehrſta/ un mannam\nBrahtain tappuſi/jo no ta KUN-\nGA irr ta wiſnam tappuſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Bet nu luhdsu es no te-\nwis weenni weenigu Luhgſchanu/\ntu ne gribbetu mannun Waigu\nRauna likt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Un wiſna ſazzija us to:\nRunna. Tad ſazzija wiſch:\nRuana jelle ar to Kehnizu Sa-\nlamanu/ jo wiſch tawu Waigu\nRauna ne liks/ ka wiſch man\nAbisagn no Sunemes par See-\nwu dohd.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "18. Un Batſeba ſazzija: Lab-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Ta nahze Batſeba pee ta\nKehnina Salamana/ Adonijus\nlabbad winnu bildinaht. Untas\nKehniſch zehlehs winnai pretti/\nun pakannijahs preekſch tahs/\npehz apſehdehs wiſch us fawn\nGehda- Krehſlu/ un dewe tat\nMahtei arrt weenu Krehſlu/ un\nta fehdeja pa winna labbo Rohku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Un wiſna ſazzija: Es\nluhdsu no tewim weenu weentgu\nmasu Luhgſchanu/ ne apkaune\nmannu Waigu. Un tas Keh-\nniſch ſazzija us to: Luhds man-\nna Mahte/ es tawu Waigu ne\napkauneschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Un wiſna ſazzija: Dohd\nAbisagn no Sunemes tawam\nBrahtam Adonijumi parSeewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Tad atbildeja tas Keh-\nniſch Salamans/ un ſazzija us\nfawu Mahti: Kapehz tu praſt\nAbisagn no Sunemes preekſch\nAdoniju? praſi preekſch winnu\narri to Walstibu/ jo wiſch ir-\nmans Brahtis/ leelaks ne ka es,\nun wiſnam irr Abjatars ta-\nPreesteris/ un Joabs Zeruja-\nDehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Un tas Kehniſch Sala-\nnans ſwebreja pee ta KUNGA\nun ſazzija: Laiman Deews fch-\nun ta darra/ teefcham Adoniju\nbuhs fcho Wahrdiu prett faw\nDſhwibu runnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Unnu/tie teefcham ka ta-\nKUNGS dſhwvo/ kas mann i-\napſtprinajs/ un mann us ma-\nNunn\n"
    }
  ],
